flowchart TD
    START([daemon_tick]) --> APIKEY{API key<br>loaded?}
    APIKEY -->|No| SKIP_EXIT([Exit: no key])
    APIKEY -->|Yes| CLIENT[Create shared<br>Anthropic client]
    CLIENT --> LOAD_STATE[Load DaemonState<br>from state.json]
    LOAD_STATE --> INGEST[Ingest Claude sessions<br>incremental parsing]
    INGEST --> GET_EVENTS[Read new events<br>since cursor]
    GET_EVENTS --> LOCK{Acquire<br>lock?}
    LOCK -->|No| LOCK_EXIT([Exit: locked])
    LOCK -->|Yes| HAS_EVENTS{New events?}

    HAS_EVENTS -->|No| CHECK_SUMMARIES
    HAS_EVENTS -->|Yes| ANALYSIS[Run detectors<br>+ Haiku batch]

    ANALYSIS --> ADVANCE[Advance cursor<br>save state]
    ADVANCE --> CHECK_SUMMARIES[Check missing<br>daily summaries]

    CHECK_SUMMARIES --> GEN_SUMMARY{Missing<br>summary?}
    GEN_SUMMARY -->|Yes| DAILY[Generate daily<br>Sonnet summary]
    DAILY --> RECS[Generate<br>recommendations]
    RECS --> COACHING_RECS[Generate coaching<br>recommendations]
    COACHING_RECS --> GEN_SUMMARY
    GEN_SUMMARY -->|No| WEEKLY{Sunday +<br>7 days since last?}

    WEEKLY -->|Yes| WEEKLY_DATA[Gather weekly data<br>+ coaching analysis]
    WEEKLY_DATA --> WEEKLY_GEN[Generate weekly<br>Sonnet digest]
    WEEKLY_GEN --> RECAL
    WEEKLY -->|No| RECAL{Recalibration<br>eligible?}

    RECAL -->|Yes| GMM[Re-fit GMM<br>on all events]
    GMM --> SAVE
    RECAL -->|No| SAVE[Save state<br>release lock]
    SAVE --> DONE([Tick complete])

    style START fill:#2d6a4f,stroke:#1b4332,color:#fff
    style DONE fill:#2d6a4f,stroke:#1b4332,color:#fff
    style SKIP_EXIT fill:#9d0208,stroke:#6a040f,color:#fff
    style LOCK_EXIT fill:#9d0208,stroke:#6a040f,color:#fff
